WEBVTT

13:31.900 --> 13:33.442
Everything is perfect.
Restore the dummy.

13:33.525 --> 13:35.484
Sir, an important matter.

13:41.567 --> 13:43.900
Are you happy that your
punishment has been postponed?

13:45.275 --> 13:46.984
Back in my school days teacher said...

13:47.025 --> 13:49.359
'Sudhakar, be honest and good
things will happen to you"

13:51.067 --> 13:52.150
I didn't get it back then.

13:52.859 --> 13:53.984
But now I get it.

14:00.067 --> 14:01.400
Hey, Roslin!

14:01.567 --> 14:03.234
You must behave well until
daddy returns from duty.

14:03.275 --> 14:06.567
Don't pester grandpa like
you do in our home.

14:07.859 --> 14:09.484
Stop intimidating a motherless child?
